import random
def row_strategy(history):
    if not history:
        return 0
    # If opponent copied our last move 80% of the time, we should vary our choices
    # to prevent prediction. Use a simple alternating pattern to break predictability.
    last_move = history[-1][0]
    if len(history) < 2:
        return 1 - last_move
    # Alternate based on previous moves to avoid patterns
    return 1 - last_move
